## 自定义表格规范（含展开行）

当表格需要展开行功能（如主从表）时，使用自定义 `<table>` 而非 DataTable 组件。

### 适用场景

| 场景 | 推荐方案 |
|------|----------|
| 标准列表（带分页） | `DataTable` |
| 大数据量（>100条） | `DataTableVirtualized` |
| 需要展开行（主从表） | 自定义 `<table>` |
| 需要复杂行内编辑 | 自定义 `<table>` |

### 完整功能清单

自定义表格应包含以下功能：

| 功能 | 必要性 | 说明 |
|------|--------|------|
| 文本搜索 | ✅ 必须 | 支持多字段模糊匹配 |
| 日期范围过滤 | ⭐ 推荐 | 使用 Calendar + Popover |
| 列排序 | ⭐ 推荐 | 点击表头切换升序/降序 |
| 全部展开/收起 | ⭐ 推荐 | 表头图标控制 |
| 展开行 | 按需 | 点击行展开子表格 |
| 列设置 | ✅ 必须 | 含 localStorage 持久化 + 恢复默认 |

### State 定义

```tsx
// 2. State
const [expandedRows, setExpandedRows] = React.useState<Record<number, boolean>>({});
const [searchTerm, setSearchTerm] = React.useState('');
const [fromDate, setFromDate] = React.useState<Date | undefined>();
const [toDate, setToDate] = React.useState<Date | undefined>();
const [selectingMode, setSelectingMode] = React.useState<'from' | 'to'>('from');
const [sortField, setSortField] = React.useState<'field1' | 'field2' | null>('field1');
const [sortDirection, setSortDirection] = React.useState<'asc' | 'desc'>('desc');
```

### 列设置持久化（自定义表格必须）

自定义表格不使用 `useDataTable`，需手动实现列偏好持久化。遵循 SSR 安全原则：`useState` 用默认值初始化，`useEffect` 中恢复 localStorage。

```tsx
import { RotateCcw } from 'lucide-react';

// 列定义
const columns = React.useMemo(() => [
  { id: 'field1', label: '字段1', hideable: false },
  { id: 'field2', label: '字段2', hideable: true },
  { id: 'field3', label: '字段3', hideable: true },
], []);

// 默认列可见性
const defaultColumnVisibility: Record<string, boolean> = React.useMemo(() => ({
  field3: false, // 默认隐藏的列
}), []);

// 列可见性状态（初始使用代码默认值，避免 SSR 水合错误）
const [columnVisibility, setColumnVisibility] = React.useState<Record<string, boolean>>(defaultColumnVisibility);

// 客户端挂载后从 localStorage 恢复偏好
const hasRestoredColVis = React.useRef(false);
React.useEffect(() => {
  if (hasRestoredColVis.current) return;
  hasRestoredColVis.current = true;
  try {
    const saved = localStorage.getItem('dt-col-vis-{tableId}');
    if (saved) setColumnVisibility(JSON.parse(saved));
  } catch {}
}, []);

// 偏好变更时自动保存
React.useEffect(() => {
  if (!hasRestoredColVis.current) return;
  try {
    localStorage.setItem('dt-col-vis-{tableId}', JSON.stringify(columnVisibility));
  } catch {}
}, [columnVisibility]);

// 检查列是否可见
const isColumnVisible = React.useCallback((columnId: string) => {
  return columnVisibility[columnId] !== false;
}, [columnVisibility]);

// 切换列可见性
const toggleColumnVisibility = React.useCallback((columnId: string) => {
  setColumnVisibility((prev) => ({
    ...prev,
    [columnId]: prev[columnId] === false ? true : false,
  }));
}, []);

// 恢复默认列设置
const resetColumnVisibility = React.useCallback(() => {
  setColumnVisibility(defaultColumnVisibility);
  try { localStorage.removeItem('dt-col-vis-{tableId}'); } catch {}
}, [defaultColumnVisibility]);

// 列设置是否已修改
const isColumnVisibilityModified = React.useMemo(() => {
  return JSON.stringify(columnVisibility) !== JSON.stringify(defaultColumnVisibility);
}, [columnVisibility, defaultColumnVisibility]);
```

**列设置 DropdownMenu（含恢复默认）：**

```tsx
<DropdownMenu>
  <DropdownMenuTrigger asChild>
    <Button variant="outline" size="sm" className="border-dashed">
      <SlidersHorizontal className="mr-2 h-4 w-4" />
      列设置
    </Button>
  </DropdownMenuTrigger>
  <DropdownMenuContent align="end" className="w-48">
    <DropdownMenuLabel>显示列</DropdownMenuLabel>
    <DropdownMenuSeparator />
    {columns.filter((col) => col.hideable).map((col) => (
      <DropdownMenuCheckboxItem
        key={col.id}
        checked={isColumnVisible(col.id)}
        onCheckedChange={() => toggleColumnVisibility(col.id)}
      >
        {col.label}
      </DropdownMenuCheckboxItem>
    ))}
    {isColumnVisibilityModified && (
      <>
        <DropdownMenuSeparator />
        <DropdownMenuItem onClick={resetColumnVisibility}>
          <RotateCcw className="mr-2 h-4 w-4" />
          恢复默认
        </DropdownMenuItem>
      </>
    )}
  </DropdownMenuContent>
</DropdownMenu>
```

**localStorage key 命名规则：** `dt-col-vis-{tableId}`，如 `dt-col-vis-coupons`。

### 过滤与排序逻辑

```tsx
// 3. Memoized values
const filteredData = React.useMemo(() => {
  let result = [...MOCK_DATA];

  // 文本搜索过滤
  if (searchTerm.trim()) {
    const term = searchTerm.toLowerCase();
    result = result.filter(
      (d) =>
        d.field1.toLowerCase().includes(term) ||
        d.field2.toLowerCase().includes(term) ||
        // 支持子项搜索
        d.children?.some((c) => c.name.toLowerCase().includes(term))
    );
  }

  // 日期范围过滤
  if (fromDate || toDate) {
    result = result.filter((d) => {
      const itemDate = new Date(d.dateField);
      if (fromDate && itemDate < fromDate) return false;
      if (toDate && itemDate > toDate) return false;
      return true;
    });
  }

  // 排序
  if (sortField) {
    result.sort((a, b) => {
      let aVal = a[sortField];
      let bVal = b[sortField];
      // 日期字段转时间戳比较
      if (sortField === 'dateField') {
        aVal = new Date(aVal).getTime();
        bVal = new Date(bVal).getTime();
      }
      if (aVal < bVal) return sortDirection === 'asc' ? -1 : 1;
      if (aVal > bVal) return sortDirection === 'asc' ? 1 : -1;
      return 0;
    });
  }

  return result;
}, [searchTerm, fromDate, toDate, sortField, sortDirection]);
```

### 排序切换逻辑

```tsx
// 切换排序
const handleSort = React.useCallback((field: SortFieldType) => {
  if (sortField === field) {
    setSortDirection((prev) => (prev === 'asc' ? 'desc' : 'asc'));
  } else {
    setSortField(field);
    setSortDirection('desc');
  }
}, [sortField]);

// 排序图标组件
const SortIcon = React.useCallback(({ field }: { field: SortFieldType }) => {
  if (sortField !== field) {
    return <ArrowUpDown className="ml-1 h-3 w-3 opacity-50" />;
  }
  return sortDirection === 'asc' ? (
    <ArrowUp className="ml-1 h-3 w-3" />
  ) : (
    <ArrowDown className="ml-1 h-3 w-3" />
  );
}, [sortField, sortDirection]);
```

### 全部展开/收起逻辑

```tsx
// 检查是否全部展开
const isAllExpanded = React.useMemo(() => {
  return filteredData.length > 0 && filteredData.every((d) => expandedRows[d.id]);
}, [filteredData, expandedRows]);

// 全部展开/收起
const toggleAllRows = React.useCallback(() => {
  if (isAllExpanded) {
    setExpandedRows({});
  } else {
    const newExpanded: Record<number, boolean> = {};
    filteredData.forEach((d) => {
      newExpanded[d.id] = true;
    });
    setExpandedRows(newExpanded);
  }
}, [isAllExpanded, filteredData]);

// 单行展开/收起
const toggleRow = React.useCallback((id: number) => {
  setExpandedRows((prev) => ({
    ...prev,
    [id]: !prev[id],
  }));
}, []);
```

### 日期过滤器 UI

```tsx
import { format } from 'date-fns';
import { Calendar as CalendarIcon, XCircle } from 'lucide-react';
import { Calendar } from '@/components/ui/calendar';
import { Popover, PopoverContent, PopoverTrigger } from '@/components/ui/popover';

// 日期过滤器显示文本
const dateFilterLabel = React.useMemo(() => {
  const fmt = (d: Date) => format(d, 'yyyy-MM-dd');
  if (fromDate && toDate) return `${fmt(fromDate)} ~ ${fmt(toDate)}`;
  if (fromDate) return `${fmt(fromDate)} 起`;
  if (toDate) return `${fmt(toDate)} 止`;
  return '选择日期范围';
}, [fromDate, toDate]);

const hasDateFilter = fromDate || toDate;

// 渲染
<Popover>
  <PopoverTrigger asChild>
    <Button variant="outline" size="sm" className="border-dashed font-normal">
      {hasDateFilter ? (
        <span onClick={(e) => { e.stopPropagation(); setFromDate(undefined); setToDate(undefined); }}>
          <XCircle className="mr-2 h-4 w-4" />
        </span>
      ) : (
        <CalendarIcon className="mr-2 h-4 w-4" />
      )}
      <span>有效期</span>
      <span className="ml-2 text-xs text-gray-500">{dateFilterLabel}</span>
    </Button>
  </PopoverTrigger>
  <PopoverContent align="start" className="w-auto p-0">
    <div className="flex flex-col">
      {/* 切换开始/结束日期标签 */}
      <div className="flex border-b">
        <button onClick={() => setSelectingMode('from')} className={cn('flex-1 px-4 py-2 ...', selectingMode === 'from' ? 'border-b-2 border-primary-600' : '')}>
          开始日期 {fromDate && <span>({format(fromDate, 'yyyy-MM-dd')})</span>}
        </button>
        <button onClick={() => setSelectingMode('to')} className={cn('flex-1 px-4 py-2 ...', selectingMode === 'to' ? 'border-b-2 border-primary-600' : '')}>
          结束日期 {toDate && <span>({format(toDate, 'yyyy-MM-dd')})</span>}
        </button>
      </div>
      {/* 日历 */}
      {selectingMode === 'from' ? (
        <Calendar mode="single" selected={fromDate} onSelect={setFromDate} />
      ) : (
        <Calendar mode="single" selected={toDate} onSelect={setToDate} />
      )}
      {/* 清除按钮 */}
      <div className="flex justify-between border-t px-3 py-2">
        <Button variant="ghost" size="sm" onClick={() => selectingMode === 'from' ? setFromDate(undefined) : setToDate(undefined)}>
          清除{selectingMode === 'from' ? '开始' : '结束'}日期
        </Button>
        <Button variant="ghost" size="sm" onClick={() => { setFromDate(undefined); setToDate(undefined); }}>
          全部清除
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </PopoverContent>
</Popover>
```

